#- That concludes the known list, this book was written on the 21st of january 2013 inspired by the release of the 1.0 map.
I am ninjajackh12 and i am proud to say im on of the last Coaldonians, I hope this was a decent book to read, please hold your 
#- memories and history dear, as it will always be important to someone, thats all for this book I hope my writings wont be in vain.
#- 